{
  "name": "consistency-qc",
  "description": "Task 2A.23 一致性 QC 闭环：视频生成完成后自动抽帧检查 face/visual 一致性，超差触发重生成或 face-swap",
  "dependencies": [
    "@/domain/schemas (VideoTask, StoryBeat, GenerationAsset)",
    "@/domain/types/result (Result, ok, err)",
    "@/infrastructure/di (container.imageApi, container.generationAssetStorage)",
    "@/shared/embedding (cosineSimilarity 代理)",
    "@/shared/error-logger (errorLogger)",
    "@/shared/utils/toast-bridge (emitToast)",
    "@/shared/constants (t)",
    "@/modules/ffmpeg-runner (generateThumbnail 抽帧)",
    "../partial-edit (startFaceSwapTask 待扩展)"
  ],
  "publicAPI": {
    "domain": [
      "QCReport",
      "FrameScore",
      "Verdict",
      "ActionTaken",
      "createEmptyQCReport",
      "computeAggregates",
      "determineVerdict",
      "shouldTriggerFallback",
      "isQCReportComplete",
      "ShotStrategy",
      "ShotStrategyType",
      "LastFrameUsage",
      "inferStrategyFromShotType",
      "createStrategy",
      "describeStrategy",
      "getStrategyThresholdMultiplier",
      "usesLastFrame",
      "isContinuousAction",
      "DriftPolicy",
      "DEFAULT_DRIFT_POLICY",
      "resolvePolicy",
      "validatePolicy",
      "shouldFallbackToFaceSwap",
      "shouldMarkManualReview"
    ],
    "services": [
      "getFaceEmbeddingProvider",
      "clearFaceEmbeddingProviderCache",
      "isFaceEmbeddingAvailable",
      "extractFaceEmbedding",
      "computeFrameSimilarity",
      "checkFrameConsistency",
      "findWorstFrame",
      "findWorstFrames",
      "filterFramesWithFace",
      "computeFrameStats",
      "runQualityCheck",
      "shouldTriggerFallback",
      "decideFallbackAction",
      "getFrameStats",
      "shouldDispatchFallback",
      "routeStrategy",
      "applyStrategyToPrompt",
      "getEffectiveThreshold",
      "describeRoutedStrategy",
      "shouldUseLastFrame",
      "getLastFrameUsage",
      "isStrategyLocked",
      "buildStrategyAwarePrompt",
      "dispatchFallback",
      "listFallbackHistory",
      "isFallbackTerminal",
      "predictNextAction"
    ],
    "hooks": [
      "useQCTrigger",
      "buildQCInput",
      "triggerQCForTask"
    ],
    "components": [
      "QCDashboardPanel"
    ]
  },
  "invariants": [
    "QC 异步非阻塞 — QC 失败不阻塞 VideoTask 完成回调，错误信息存于 QCReport.error",
    "Embedding provider 可插拔 — face-embedding-service 通过 FaceEmbeddingProvider 接口抽象，ONNX → VLM → noop 三级降级",
    "Verdict 由阈值决定 — determineVerdict(minScore, policy) 严格按 warningThreshold/criticalThreshold 判定",
    "重试计数不可重置 — QCReport.retryCount 单调递增，actionTaken 字段记录最终动作",
    "ShotStrategy 不改 prompt 语义 — applyStrategyToPrompt 仅追加约束指令，不修改原始 prompt 内容",
    "QCReport 持久化于 StoryBeat.qcReport — QC 完成后存于 StoryBeat，新 QC 覆盖旧 report",
    "Fallback 链式降级 — regenerate → face-swap → manual_review，不可跳过 regenerate（除非 maxRegenerateAttempts=0）",
    "不修改原视频 — QC 仅读取视频帧，regenerate/face-swap 创建新 VideoTask",
    "face embedding 走 @/shared/embedding 代理导出，不直接导入 @/infrastructure/embedding"
  ]
}
